{"tid":431222,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［日本既匠人匠心］TeamLab","createTime":"2017-10-10T13:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T06:52:29.000Z","uid":18720,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"90e82775f55a0d51c5f6128128956f310e74efc8","tid":431222,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的 TeamLab被選為年度十大必睇展覽之一<br />\n自從睇完啲demo片我就覺得點都要搵個weekend早啲起身去狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接去圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/212618_521015afd0c4461b4b48d54d3168aa3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F212618_521015afd0c4461b4b48d54d3168aa3a.jpg&h=5ddf427c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/212619_9ae534cca143c0dd9fa64cbfe7de61b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F212619_9ae534cca143c0dd9fa64cbfe7de61b9.jpg&h=b4b8131a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/212620_df935fb6bac3a0ebc2a6e330631e1c0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F212620_df935fb6bac3a0ebc2a6e330631e1c0c.jpg&h=04c43296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/212712_37a6004238a6090da68e397de0c30486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F212712_37a6004238a6090da68e397de0c30486.jpg&h=e6b5fcca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/212713_94f3271c83ee87171e58c1db5efbbae8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F212713_94f3271c83ee87171e58c1db5efbbae8.jpg&h=4ef26fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/212714_94f3271c83ee87171e58c1db5efbbae8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F212714_94f3271c83ee87171e58c1db5efbbae8.jpg&h=bb079672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實見樣既相係影得最好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我比兩條demo link比大家睇下個效果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cEMniCKnOD0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcEMniCKnOD0&d=rClWMGmvypBpYy8zADHpI4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=058b7a31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cEMniCKnOD0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tPKBDPWOtGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtPKBDPWOtGk&d=rClWMGmvypBpYy8zADHpI4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=aaf15603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tPKBDPWOtGk</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都去左睇呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎交流下啲靚相<br />\n<br />\n佢只能收VISA/wechat pay 呢方面要注意⚠️<br />\n同埋香港學生證都有效 票價就會變成$160<br />\n<br />\n可以平日去當然最好 唔得既話最好weekend有咁早得咁早出發 <br />\n以免好似利東街影月亮咁 影到幾百個人頭做背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d80618a8115f102c97b856f7500963550533100","tid":431222,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/215908_4ea16698bf571976e182745376a04fae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F215908_4ea16698bf571976e182745376a04fae.jpg&h=9df08039&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95ce008555e5b46e09e27fc38bb39320d0c16939","tid":431222,"uid":18720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:59:43.000Z","msg":